OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774019480
OL,3,CHow man's Meningitis diagnosis aged 6
OL,4,Chas helped develop life-saving vaccine
OL,6,FA man from Devon who was part of the
OL,7,Fresearch for the Meningitis B vaccine
OL,8,Fthat is currently being used after the
OL,9,Foutbreak in Kent, has urged people to
OL,10,Fbe hyper vigilant over the deadly
OL,11,Fillness.
OL,13,FGeorge Fitzgerald was struck down with
OL,14,FMeningitis as a child and his parents
OL,15,Fgave permission for tissue taken from
OL,16,Fhim at the time to be used as part of
OL,17,Fgenetic research for the vaccine.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
