FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774019480
OL,3,CHow man's Meningitis diagnosis aged 6
OL,4,Chas helped develop life-saving vaccine
OL,6,FHe was just six he time when he was
OL,7,Frushed to hospital 25 years ago. His
OL,8,Flife hung in the balance for several
OL,9,Fdays.
OL,11,FSpeaking about going into hospital on
OL,12,FChristmas Day in 2000, George said: "I
OL,13,Fjust remember it being very confusing,
OL,14,Fnot really knowing what was going on
OL,15,Fand I didn't understand the
OL,16,Fseriousness of it all."
OL,18,FGeorge's father David had rushed him
OL,19,Fto Derriford Hospital. He said: "It
OL,20,Fwas a very difficult time and highly
OL,21,Femotional now to speak of it.
OL,26,@tD@eOUxD@WO]{D@aOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774019480
OL,3,CHow man's Meningitis diagnosis aged 6
OL,4,Chas helped develop life-saving vaccine
OL,6,F"I remember him laying beside me on
OL,7,Fthe bed. He didn't show the signs of
OL,8,FMeningitis, there was no rash, he was
OL,9,Ffairly mobile.
OL,11,F"The hospital worked incredibly hard,
OL,12,Fespecially when they found out they
OL,13,Fhit the emergency button and took him
OL,14,Fto the high dependency ward."
OL,16,FGeorge's mum Karen Fitzgerald said: "I
OL,17,Fwas told it was Meningitis B, there
OL,18,Fwas no vaccine, no cure and one of the
OL,19,Fworst things was, I asked, 'What's the
OL,20,Fbottom line?', and they said he had
OL,21,Fabout 8 to 12 hours left.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@]O]xD@eOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774019480
OL,3,CHow man's Meningitis diagnosis aged 6
OL,4,Chas helped develop life-saving vaccine
OL,6,F"That was the worst moment of my life."
OL,8,FAs he began to recover, George's
OL,9,Fparents were asked if they were
OL,10,Fwilling to allow a sample of his DNA
OL,11,Fto be taken to be used in genetic
OL,12,Fresearch for a new vaccine.
OL,14,FTen years later the family received a
OL,15,Fletter from the University of
OL,16,FSheffield Hospital saying that thanks
OL,17,Fto the contribution of George and
OL,18,Fothers, a new vaccine had been created
OL,19,Fagainst Meningitis B.
OL,26,@nD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774019480
OL,3,CHow man's Meningitis diagnosis aged 6
OL,4,Chas helped develop life-saving vaccine
OL,6,FSpeaking about his DNA being used to
OL,7,Fhelp create the vaccine, 31-year-old
OL,8,FGeorge said: "It's very humbling, it's
OL,9,Fquite nice to know that it's doing
OL,10,Fsome good."
OL,12,FHis father David said: "I don't think
OL,13,Fwe understood the importance."
OL,15,FMum Karen added: "Sheffield University
OL,16,Fwrote to let us know they had created
OL,17,Fa vaccine.
OL,26,@pD@NOUrD@KO]tD@XOUuD@^O]wD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774019480
OL,3,CHow man's Meningitis diagnosis aged 6
OL,4,Chas helped develop life-saving vaccine
OL,6,F"That was quite a special moment. We
OL,7,Fdon't know what they did with the
OL,8,Ftissue they received but it's a great
OL,9,Ffeeling."
OL,11,F"The NHS saved his life, now there is
OL,12,Fa vaccine and I would urge everybody
OL,13,Fto get that vaccine."
OL,15,FGeorge said: "You need to look after
OL,16,Fyourself, the only thing that saved me
OL,17,Fwas how healthy I was, and I owe that
OL,18,Fto my mum."
OL,26,@qD@IO]sD@AOUuD@UO]wD@NOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
