OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774019480
OL,3,CHow man's Meningitis diagnosis aged 6
OL,4,Chas helped develop life-saving vaccine
OL,6,FThe vaccine created with George's help
OL,7,Fis now being used in the areas where
OL,8,Fthe Meningitis outbreak is at its
OL,9,Fworst, hoping to reduce the risk of
OL,10,Fpeople living getting the potentially
OL,11,Ffatal illness.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
